(1735, 1, '2017-05-08 14:29:37', '2017-05-08 14:29:37', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em>Blue Drum Activist Summer Camp 2017</em></strong></span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Power of networked practice</strong>\nGlencree, Co. Wicklow\nSaturday &amp; Sunday, June 17/18 June 2017</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1693\" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/COF-Activity-Camp-Knockree-340715-Group-17-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /></p>\nThe aim of the Camp in 2017 is to build bridges and connections because we know that the experience of one can be of help to the other.  Are you embedded activists/artists who are working deeply with the ecologies of people and place to shape new inter-connectivity.\n\n<strong>The Camp has 4 parts:</strong>\n\n-Inspiration:  <em>International Community Arts</em> <em>Festival</em> (TBC).\n-Facilitated process (3 hours)  to imagine what networked practice could look like.\n-Cluster Workshops\n<ul>\n 	<li>Creativity and agency in work for environmental justice.<img class=\"wp-image-1692 alignright\" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/COF-Activity-Camp-Group-Knockree-340715-15-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"135\" /></li>\n 	<li>Creativity and agency in work with public participation networks (PPNs).</li>\n 	<li>Creativity and agency in urban and rural community regeneration.</li>\n</ul>\n-Facilitated process (3 hours) that will deliver a <em>Culture Contact</em> Charter for 2017/2018\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>This is a creative camp for activists, artists &amp; especially for YOUR local group!</strong></p>\n<strong> </strong>\n\n<strong>When &amp; Where</strong>\n\nGlencree Centre for Peace and Reconciliation, Glencree, Co Wicklow\n\n<strong>Suggested contribution towards costs are: </strong>40 Euro waged, 20 Euro unwaged (incl. children), 1 Euro Asylum Seekers. This includes the accommodation for 1 night in a shared room and vegetarian food.\n\nBrilliant childcare available (please let us know in advance).\n\n<strong> </strong>\n\n<strong>Registration: </strong>Places are limited, please register now: <a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.ie/e/activistartist-summer-camp-tickets-32688812117\">https://www.eventbrite.ie/e/activistartist-summer-camp-tickets-32688812117</a>\n\n<strong>With any questions just contact Ed or Eleanor at </strong><a href=\"mailto:blue.drum@yahoo.com\"><strong>blue.drum@yahoo.com</strong></a><strong> or 087 2334931</strong>\n\n<strong><em> </em></strong>', 'Blue Drum Activist Summer Camp 2017', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'blue-drum-activist-summer-camp-2017', '', '', '2017-05-08 14:29:37', '2017-05-08 14:29:37', '', 0, 'http://alact.ie/?p=1735', 0, 'post', '', 0),
