(1780, 1, '2017-05-14 23:04:23', '2017-05-14 23:04:23', '<!--\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-121 alignright\" src=\"http://ala-ct.ie/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/ALa-Youth-and-Family-Module-Lifecourse-Building-NUIG-8-1024x768-1.jpg\" alt=\"ALa-Youth-and-Family-Module-Lifecourse-Building-NUIG-8-1024x768-1-272x182\" width=\"376\" height=\"282\" /><img class=\"alignleft\" />-->\r\n\r\nALâ Participatory Theatre has since 2004 continuously expanded and so to our Committee Structure. So much so ALâ has established two divisions, Community Workshop and Theatre for Change each with its own committee and coordinator reporting to the Managing Committee. These are two separate entities but are quite interdependent upon each other with many of the participants of the Community Workshops group participating in the activities of the Theatre for Change, formerly known as Outreach and Training.\r\n<!-- Each coordinating officer reports back to the overall management committee of the overall organisation. ALâ has recently become a Limited by Guarantee organisation in the last few months. This was done because of the continued growth of ALâ.-->\r\nALâ headquarters is currently at 83 Castlepark Ballybane. In the near future, we are hoping to find a new home for the organisation that will reflect the growing nature of participatory theatre in the Ballybane area of Galway. Below you can see the structure of our organisation and who the officers are in the organisation.\r\n<!--\r\n<img class=\"&quot; aligncenter\" src=\"http://ala-ct.ie/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Structure1.png\" width=\"693\" height=\"321\" />\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 18.0pt;\">--></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"team\">\r\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-align: center; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px;\"><strong>Our team leaders</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\"><strong>Management Committee</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"team-item\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1465\" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Brian-Donnelly2.jpg\" alt=\"Brian Donnely - ALâ Chairperson\" width=\"135\" height=\"196\" />\r\n<div class=\"team-title\"><strong>Brian Donnely</strong>\r\nALâ Chairperson</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"team-item\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1348\" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Louie-Maguire-1-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"136\" height=\"157\" />\r\n<div class=\"team-title\"><strong>Louie Maguire</strong>\r\nALâ Treasurer</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"team-item\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\" size-full wp-image-1338\" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Marie_-Aherne_2-1.png\" alt=\"Marie Aherne - ALâ Assistant treasurer\" width=\"140\" height=\"146\" />\r\n<div class=\"team-title\"><strong>Marie Aherne</strong>\r\nALâ Assistant treasurer</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"team-item\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\" size-full wp-image-1332\" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Tanisha-1.png\" alt=\"Tanisha Geoghegan - ALâ Public relations coordinator\" width=\"140\" height=\"170\" />\r\n<div class=\"team-title\"><strong>Tanisha Geoghegan</strong>\r\nALâ Public relations coordinator</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"team-item\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-1351 \" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ferdia-Watts.jpg\" alt=\"Ferdia Watts Committee Member\" width=\"137\" height=\"140\" />\r\n<div class=\"team-title\"><strong>Ferdia Watts</strong>\r\nCommittee Member</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"team-item\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-1351 \" src=\"http://localhost/alact.ie/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Amber-Watts.jpg\" alt=\"Amber Watts Committee Member\" width=\"137\" height=\"140\" />\r\n<div class=\"team-title\"><strong>Amber Watts</strong>\r\nCommittee Member</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"team\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\"><strong>Coordinators</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"te